---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Games · Lincon Vidal"
  description="Games by Lincon Vidal."
>
  <section class="page-hero compact-hero games-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">games</p>
    <h1>Mostly Pinote for now.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      A small bike game about timing, weight, and bad landings.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section split-section">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">pinote</p>
      <h2>The bike keeps crashing.</h2>
    </div>
    <article class="prose section-copy">
      <p>
        That is the thing I am trying to get right: weight, timing, landings, and crashes that are readable enough to be funny.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
